dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Green County, WI 2017
dc_description_s: These polygon and line data layers represent hydrography for Green County, Wisconsin in 2017. They are feature classes within the geodatabase, Green_Hydro_2017.gdb. The freatures included in this geodatabase are' GREEN_BREAKLINES_2011', 'GREEN_HYDRO_UNK_LINE' , 'GREEN_HYDRO_UNK_POLY', and 'GREEN_HYDRO2_UNK_POLY',
uw_supplemental_s: This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017. This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.greencountywi.org/179/Downloadable-GIS-Data-Forms
